How to build DIRAC documentation
=================================

1. Create DIRAC client environment by an appropriate
   source bashrc

2. Go to the Documentation directory of the DIRAC source code repository
   cd DIRAC/docs/

3. Run the documentation building script
   READTHEDOCS=True make html

3.1 to run incremental builds after files have changed, only run

   make html

3.2 The automatic creation of the CodeDocumentation and CommandDocumentation can be run from the docs/Tools
    folders with either

    ./MakeDoc.py [-dd[d]]
    ./buildScriptsDocs.py [-dd[d]]
